                                                >cookie_consent</td
                                            ><td class='p-2'>airtravel.es</td
                                            ><td class='p-2'
                                                >Guardar preferencias de
                                                consentimiento (banner cookies)</td
                                            ><td class='p-2'>1 año</td></tr
                                        >
                                        <tr class='border-b border-green-100'
